{"tid":1511394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懶理手足生死，荃灣廣場鎖淨半道門！","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:21:30.000Z","uid":182997,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5da89220c3c580eddfeece4e308435d1675076f4","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"終於有時間講返25/8嘅周邊嘢。<br />\n<br />\n新鴻基出賣港人眾所周知，而佢旗下嘅荃灣廣場亦都唔例外。當日接近五點，警賊宣布會喺短時間內清場，荃灣廣場竟然將九成通往大街/行人天橋嘅出入口鎖咗，有人打電話去CS，講到明有緊急情況，商場竟然無視！<br />\n<br />\n封鎖（一）<br />\n商場派保安喺大會堂上面，通往商場嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>行人天橋攔截市民</strong></span>，話「前面個入口無開」，不過完全被市民無視，有人大聲屌保安<br />\n<br />\n封鎖（二）<br />\n行人天橋入口，Pizzaexpress對出，有三度門，當時有位目測三十歲嘅工作人員哥哥<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經鎖咗兩度門，仲打算鎖埋最後一度</span></strong>，市民趕及喺最後一度被鎖之前喝止，要求佢立即開返門，佢請示上頭之後，開返晒三度門<br />\n*要講返句，哥哥其實好有禮貌<br />\n<br />\n封鎖（三）<br />\n商場最離譜，係竟然將地下楊屋道<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全部五度門鎖起</strong></span>，當然已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>放緊催淚彈</strong></span>，好多手足想入商場都入唔到。有市民打電話去CS，亦有人同保安理論，其中一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>廢老保安大聲還口</strong></span>，令到在場嘅人嬲上加嬲，而其他保安以「叫咗經理嚟」為藉口推搪。<br />\n<br />\n唔夠十五分鐘，出面愈來愈多人退到商場入口外，推門失敗後無奈離去。有市民再打電話去CS，講到明有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>緊急情況發生</strong></span>，要求佢地立即開門，結果商場都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無開門</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n雖然事後得知，示威者並冇因為荃灣廣場鎖門走避不及而導致被捕或受傷，但事前根本無人知會發生咩事，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">將九成出入口封鎖，絕對可以造成嚴重後果</span></span></strong>，而知道有緊急情況都唔開門更加係冷血表現！<br />\n<br />\n站喺佢地角度諗，商場咁嘅安排對自己公關絕無好處，實例證明好多商場因為放示威者入、拒黑警於門外，而受到公眾認同，完全唔明佢地咁做有咩好處，好大機會係出於政治原因，懶理市民生死！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣廣場今次算你好彩！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"afefee76bf67e4ca92044a141de4ef31cdd29e21","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fe3ea48d9c76b43f5765a44f63988b34088fca1e","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"579014a1b22ac785686e332f656576e6d4c0c21a","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b0a6fdc91a32040dbf186e087b28be40bda2adec","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ae5124e238ea75b4aa66e046f2e7c8515d1358f8","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2e87020af64eeabe8674d32c88dec662f261c14f","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0dd8ad3ec9a73f3a8081c295ad22b60b686abfd4","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"030c6bf0f7640b36d9f769e6a085b42812af06be","tid":1511394,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"25f0361996090ab84b565fa0